<h2>Top things to do in Vietnam/ Best activities in Vietnam</h2>

<h3>Cruise the Mekong Delta</h3>
<p>The wooden classic-style boats in the Mekong Delta offer a one-of-a-kind experience that any of us would enjoy. Private cabins offer spectacular views. This is undoubtedly one of the nicest experiences you can have in Vietnam.</p>

<h2>Visiting the Temple of Literature</h2>
<p>Emperor Le Thanh Tong erected the Temple of Literature in 1070. It was a university devoted to the Chinese philosopher Confucius. Six years later, it was transformed into an academic institution. This is an excellent destination to visit on your Vietnam tour. </p>

<h3>Snorkeling on Cham Island</h3>
<p>You may add some adventure to your journey by selecting the snorkelling option on Cham Island. When selecting Vietnam packages from India, you may check to see if this option is included.</p>

<h3>Crawl through the Cu Chi Tunnel Network</h3>
<p>Cu Chi Tunnel Network is well-known for its subterranean tunnel network, which was built in 1940 during the French-American War. This massive network of tunnels, spanning 250 km, was built to facilitate communication throughout the conflict. </p>

